Why is my Ad rejected?

Ad rejection reasons are unique to each ad. Some common reasons include incorrect conversion tracking for a tCPA campaign or typographical errors. Ad Support will inform you of the specific reason via your email. For more details, you can check out this article: [My ad got rejected. My Ad did not spend the daily budget

There could be several reasons why your ad did not spend the daily budget. It might be due to low audience reach, high competition, or ad relevance issues. To get a more detailed analysis, you can check your campaign settings and performance metrics. If you need further assistance, please contact our support team at adsupport@newsbreak.com.
